  80,1,"zhr altaghayur walebws fi wajh alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm, wa'aerid li'ajal 'ana al'aemaa eabd allah bin 'am maktum ja'ah mstrshda, wakan alrasul salaa allah ealayh wasalam mnshghla bidaewat kibar quraysh 'iilaa al'islam"
