  80,33,"f'idha ja'at sayhatan yawm alqiamat alty tsmm min hwlha alasmae, yawm yfrr almar' lhwl dhlk alyawm min akhyh, wa'umah wabyh, wazawjih wbnyh. likuli wahid minhum ywmydh 'amr yshghlh wymneh min alanshghal bghyrh"
