  80,38,"wjwh 'ahl alnaeim fi dhalik alyawm mstnyrt, msrwrt frht, wawujuh 'ahl aljahim mzlmt mswddat, taghashaaha dhll. 'uwlayik almwswfwn bhdha alwsf hum aladhin kafaruu binaeam allah wkdhdhabu bayath, wtjrwu ealaa mharmh balfjwr waltghyan"
