  83,7,"hqa 'iina masir alfujjar wamawahum lafi dyq, wama 'adrak ma hdha aldyq? 'iinah sijn muqim waeadhab alym, wahu ma kutib lahum almasir 'ilyh, maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs"
  83,8,"haqana 'iina masir alfujjar wamawahum lafi dyq, wama 'adrak ma hdha aldyq? 'iinah sijn muqim waeadhab alym, wahu ma kutib lahum almasir 'ilyh, maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs"
