  85,10,"'in aladhin haraquu almuminin walmuminat balnar; lysrfwhm ean din allh, thuma lam ytwbu, falahum fi alakhirat eadhab jhnm, walahum aleadhab alshadid almhrq"
  85,11,"'in aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu al'aemal alsalhat, lahum janaat tajri min taht qswrha alanhar, dhlk alfawz alezym"
